title:
The Golden Honor Roll
            
            
                
                    - Student Philanthropy
main_content: So far during the 2023–24 school year, over 190 students have pledged to Keep Cal Golden by giving back to the on-campus causes of their choice. We are so thankful for each and every one of our student supporters!
